{
  "stem": "5255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each member of the family had to bury their own members of the family that got killed in that particular basement.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it happens-- that happens in many basements in the city of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not only in the Jewish neighborhoods but in the non-Jewish neighborhoods, as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they weren't killed because they were Jews, it's just a unfortunate-- fortune of wars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the artillery came this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Artillery-- all around Warsaw, there was-- encircled the city of Warsaw-- and the artillery were shooting down into the city just everywhere.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to bury our own dead, because at that time nobody wanted to accept Polish money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even if you had the money you couldn't get anybody to work for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to take our own cadavers-- members-- and put them on pushcarts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And taking the pushcart to the Warsaw cemetery-- Jewish cemetery-- digging a common grave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we dug a grave for 37 people from our building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we buried them according to the Jewish law, as a group in their clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first experience that I had in the war of a personal nature.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mind wasn't functioning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had just to do things because this was the things to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no past.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no future.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was just the present.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What do we do now?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After we buried our dead we were sitting shiva according to the Jewish customs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the whole building was sitting shiva.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a tragedy, enormous proportions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We lost our most important people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my-- thank God, Grandma was alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she took care of us, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she cooked for us, she baked for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
